Class ConverterUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.axis2.databinding.utils.ConverterUtil

  • public class ConverterUtil
extends Object
    Converter methods to go from 1. simple type -> String 2. simple type -> Object 3. String -> simpletype 4. Object list -> array
